	<li class="comment odd alt thread-even depth-1" id="comment-7206">
	<article >

		
		<header class="comment-header">
			<p class="comment-author">
				<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e626621d7b6054a4f491fc974063d8ae?s=48&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e626621d7b6054a4f491fc974063d8ae?s=96&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' loading='lazy'/><span itemprop="name">DeerSpotter</span> 			</p>

